15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 11-203 of Title 70, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. Human growth and development curriculum shall be taught in
20 the public schools of this state. Human growth and development
21 education shall include, but is not limited to:
22 1. Human biology related to pregnancy;
23 2. Human development inside of a womb;
